data.description: 6610 Ridgecrest Blvd., Inyokern, CA, 93527. Discover your ideal home on this peaceful property. With 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and 2.56 Acres of land on a paved road, this home is a comfortable haven for your family. Property has new interior paint.  This property is positioned adjacent to BLM land which provides protection over natural, cultural, and historical resources so that you can marvel at the majestic mountain view from your windows. Double insulation and evaporative cooling ensure comfort year-round, keeping the interior the way you like it. Zoned as a horse property, it's perfect for equestrian enthusiasts. Water is conveniently sourced from a well, piped in the back, and a fully fenced yard with wide access gates adds security. The power/electricity is on a meter, ensuring accurate usage tracking. Stay connected with high-speed internet, enabling you to embrace simple living with these essential features. Don't forget to take a virtual tour and schedule your showing today.
